features: 【Package Includes】: 32 watercolor floral stationery paper (7.5” x 10.4”), 16 envelopes (4.3” x 7.8”) and 16 seal stickers (0.78” in diameter). 4 floral designs, double sided printing.

【Superior Quality】：Our stationary paper are made of quality material. Letter writing Paper and envelopes are compatible with inkjet or laser printers. Perfect for use with ballpoint, gel pens, fountain pen, pencil, etc.

【Perfect Pattern Design】：These stationary set is perfect for who loves to write handwritten letters. The letter writing paper with some decoration at corner and slightly color background makes calligraphy or writing clear but elegant and impressive.

【Multi-Purpose】：Printed on both sides with decorative watercolor designs, our letter writing paper is unique to create your Invitations, Anniversaries, Graduations, Announcements and your letter for family or friends.

【Easy to Use】: Each designed envelope and letter paper is individually packaged for easy differentiation and selection. Each envelope comes with a seal sticker to give you a more convenient experience
body.description: Features: Material: Smooth uncoated recycled paper. Size: Stationery Paper – 7.5” x 10.4” (190x265 mm), Envelope – 4.3” x 7.8” (110x200 mm) Package includes: 8pcs stationeries, 4pcs envelopes and 4pcs seal stickers of each pattern, 4 designs assorted. Each set of letter sheet and matched envelopes are packed in an individual poly bag and then 4 different bags put into another poly bag.
